phabet's%20Waymo%3C%2Fa%3E%20operates%20robotaxis%20without%20safety%20drivers%20present%20in%20the%20vehicles.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-learned-about-tesla-robotaxis-from-early-access-riders-videos-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETesla's%20robotaxis%20in%20Austin%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20currently%20limited%20to%2010%20to%2020%20Model%20Ys%20and%20have%20safety%20operators%20in%20the%20front%20passenger%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaymo%20has%20deployed%20more%20than%201%2C500%20robotaxis%20in%20multiple%20US%20cities%20as%20of%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scale%20of%20expansion%20in%20Austin%20and%20the%20phase%20of%20Tesla's%20robotaxi%20service%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20and%20Phoenix%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20that's%20testing%20with%20or%20without%20early%20riders%20%E2%80%94%20remains%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-autonomous-vehicle-federal-regulation-trump-white-house-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eregulatory%20landscape%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20autonomous%20ride-hailing%20services%20in%20California%20is%20more%20extensive%20than%20in%20Texas%2C%20where%20companies%20don't%20need%20specific%20permits%20to%20operate%20autonomous%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20California%2C%20companies%20must%20apply%20for%20permits%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Motor%20Vehicles%20and%20the%20California%20Public%20Utilities%20Commission%20to%20begin%20testing%20autonomous%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CPUC%20granted%20Tesla%20what's%20called%20a%20transportation%20charter%20permit%20in%20March.%20It's%20a%20key%20milestone%20for%20the%20company%20to%20start%20a%20ride-hailing%20business%2C%20but%20the%20permit%20doesn't%20allow%20Tesla%20to%20operate%20quite%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-focuses-cheaper-rides-routes-delivery-new-features-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUber%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flyft-aims-at-uber-with-price-lock-feature-surge-pricing-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELyft%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20let%20alone%20deploy%20autonomous%20vehicles.%20Instead%2C%20it%20allows%20Tesla%20to%20provide%20a%20transportation%20service%20with%20its%20own%20vehicles%20and%20only%20for%20its%20employees%2C%20almost%20like%20an%20internal%20chauffeur%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaseen%20Shamim%2C%20a%20CPUC%20spokesperson%2C%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20email%20that%20Tesla%20hasn't%20applied%20for%20%26quot%3Bany%20new%20CPUC-issued%20operating%20authorities%26quot%3B%20as%20of%20Thursday%20afternoon.%20When%20asked%20how%20long%20the%20approval%20process%20would%20take%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20agency%20%26quot%3Bcannot%20speculate%20on%20process%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20California%20DMV%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20email%20that%20Tesla%20has%20held%20a%20permit%20to%20test%20autonomous%20vehicles%20on%20public%20roads%20with%20a%20safety%20driver%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20date%2C%20Tesla%20has%20not%20applied%20for%20either%20a%20driverless%20testing%20or%20deployment%20permit%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20meaning%20Tesla%20can't%20yet%20test%20without%20a%20safety%20operator%20inside%20the%20vehicle%20or%20deploy%20robotaxis%20for%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b2ee2b5-62dc-44dd-99bd-437270d5a529%5C%22%3EThe%20'theater'%20behind%20Tesla's%20robotaxi%20expansion%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGene%20Munster%2C%20a%20Tesla%20investor%20and%20managing%20partner%20at%20Deepwater%20Asset%20Management%20who%20covers%20robotaxis%2C%20said%20in%20his%20%26quot%3BPressure%20Points%26quot%3B%20podcast%20that%20the%20expansion%20news%20brings%20further%20investor%20%26quot%3Boptimism%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20clear%20sign%20that%20Tesla's%20stock%20will%20largely%20be%20dependent%20on%20the%20company's%20progress%20with%20autonomy%20and%20less%20so%20ab