ved%20from%20Maui%20to%20Pohnpei%2C%20an%20island%20that's%20part%20of%20the%20Federated%20States%20of%20Micronesia%2C%20in%202018.%3Cp%3EBuz%20Moffett.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBuz%20Moffett%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Liz%2C%20moved%20from%20Hawaii%20to%20Pohnpei%20in%20Micronesia%20in%202018.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20wanted%20to%20slow%20down%2C%20work%20less%2C%20and%20be%20away%20from%20the%20tourist%20crowds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20sometimes%20go%20without%20fresh%20veggies%20or%20dairy%20as%20the%20supply%20ship%20comes%20every%20two%20to%20three%20weeks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Buz%20Moffett%2C%2063%2C%20who%20moved%20from%20Hawaii%20to%20Pohnpei%2C%20an%20island%20in%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%20that's%20part%20of%20the%20Federated%20States%20of%20Micronesia%2C%20with%20his%20wife%20in%202018.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20time%20I%20visited%20Pohnpei%20was%20in%202006.%20An%20Australian%20friend%20suggested%20that%20I%20check%20out%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-quit-corporate-jobs-city-hotel-beach-surfing-siargao-philippines-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esurf%3C%2Fa%3E%20camp%20there.%20He%20thought%20I'd%20love%20the%20place%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20was%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20island%20is%20stunning%2C%20the%20people%20are%20warm%2C%20and%20it%20offers%20world-class%20waves%2C%20great%20fishing%2C%20and%20incredible%20diving.%20Over%20the%20next%2010%20years%2C%20I%20went%20back%20there%20almost%20every%20other%20year.%20Eventually%2C%20my%20wife%2C%20Liz%2C%20started%20joining%20me%20on%20my%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20day%20in%202017%2C%20she%20approached%20me%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20could%20live%20here.%26quot%3B%20By%20then%2C%20I%20was%20in%20my%20mid-50s%20and%20ready%20to%20slow%20down%20%E2%80%94%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20continue%20to%20work%20myself%20to%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20born%20in%20California%20but%20raised%20%3Cspan%3Ein%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhawaiian-local-thoughts-feelings-about-tourism-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Hawaii%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Being%20in%20the%20real%20estate%20industry%2C%20I%20always%20dreamed%20of%20retiring%20somewhere%20quieter%2C%20more%20like%20the%20Maui%20I%20knew%20from%20the%20late%20'60s%20and%20early%20'70s%2C%20with%20fewer%20visitors%20and%20a%20slower%20pace%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe'd%20considered%20moving%20to%20Molokai%2C%20but%20Liz%20felt%20it%20was%20too%20close%20to%20Maui.%20She%20knew%20I'd%20just%20hop%20on%20my%20boat%20back%20and%20keep%20working.%20We%20decided%20Pohnpei%2C%20an%20eight-hour%20flight%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhonolulu-hawaii-oahu-most-surprising-things-first-trip-photos-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHonolulu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20the%20right%20place%20for%20us%20to%20start%20our%20new%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20sunset%20in%20Pohnpei.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686780d785e81483682d67bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20of%20the%20sunset%20in%20Pohnpei.%3Cp%3EBuz%20Moffett.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20putting%20out%20feelers%20with%20a%20few%20friends%20about%20finding%20a%20place%20to%20rent.%20As%20foreigners%2C%20we%20can't%20own%20land%20in%20Micronesia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20enough%2C%20a%20friend%20of%20mine%20who%20runs%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fpohnpeisurfclub.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurfing%20and%20diving%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20Pohnpei%20called%20me%20and%20told%20me%20he%20had%20found%20the%20perfect%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20us%20that%20it%20might%20be%20better%20than%20his%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20has%20a%20nice%20waterfront%20home.%20We%20didn't%20even%20see%20a%20picture%3B%20we%20just%20jumped%20on%20it.%20Turns%20out%2C%20he%20was%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20two-bedroom%2C%20one-bathroom%20home%20right%20by%20the%20ocean.%20Rent%20is%20%241%2C500%20a%20month%2C%20and%20we%20have%20wonderful%20landlords%20who%20treat%20us%20like%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20been%20living%20in%20Pohnpei%20ever%20since%2C%20with%20a%20two-year%20gap%20during%20the%20pandemic%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e2ee1e60-3d32-421c-a27e-501428775089%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20good%20kind%20of%20busy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20become%20part%20of%20the%20community%20and%20have%20embraced%20the%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20not%20working%2C%20finding%20an%20activity%20to%20fill%20your%20time%20is%20really%20important.%20Somehow%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20almost%20busier%20now%20than%20I%20was%20when%20I%20was%20working%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20just%20a%20healthier%20type%20of%20busy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20holding%20up%20his%20catch.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6867851d3d5881a51c1cb94f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMoffett%20says%20he%20spends%20most%20of%20his%20days%20fishing%20and%20smoking%20fish.%3Cp%3EBuz%20Moffett.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20day%2C%20I'll%20start%20with%20coffee%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F74-year-old-exercise-routine-longevity-daily-strength-cardio-workouts-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworkout%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20then%20return%20a%20few%20calls%20and%20emails%20before%20heading%20down%20to%20the%20harbor%20by%2010%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ice%20up%20the%20boat%20and%20refuel%20b