he's%20on%20the%20hunt%20for%20what%20she%20thinks%20could%20be%20a%20multimillion-dollar%20business%20in%20consumer%20tech.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20generation%20of%20apps%20we%20use%20to%20find%20love%20may%20not%20look%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-dating-startups-and-apps-disrupting-the-industry-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edating%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%20we're%20used%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmber%20Atherton%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20consumer-focused%20venture%20capital%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frising-stars-venture-capital-tech-startups-2023-11%23amber-atherton-patron-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPatron%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20thinks%20artificial%20intelligence%20will%20dramatically%20change%20how%20we%20meet%20people%20online.%20Instead%20of%20swiping%20through%20profiles%20or%20scrolling%20through%20a%20feed%2C%20platforms%20in%20the%20AI%20era%20will%20use%20what%20they%20know%20about%20you%20to%20find%20new%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStartups%20are%20building%20what%20Atherton%20dubs%20%26quot%3Brelationship%20OS%26quot%3B%20platforms.%20They're%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fy-combinator-yc-demo-day-spring-ai-agent-startups-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eagentic%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20(such%20as%20autonomous%20assistants)%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20more%20relevant%20connections%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmine%20your%20network%2C%26quot%3B%20Atherton%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20an%20agentic%20social%20network%20basically%20that%20I%20think%20is%20going%20to%20emerge%20that%20is%20not%20packaged%20as%20a%20dating%20app%2C%26quot%3B%20Atherton%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20packaged%20more%20as%20this%20operating%20system%20for%20relationships.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20not%20just%20for%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20being%20that%20it's%20always%20on%2C%20evergreen%20AI-assisted%20network%20that%20can%20surface%20connections%20that%20are%20relevant%20for%20friendship%2C%20romance%2C%20professional%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Atherton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20startups%20that%20Atherton%20mentioned%20as%20examples%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-professional-networking-startups-linkedin-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBoardy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20hails%20itself%20as%20an%20%26quot%3BAI%20super%20connector%26quot%3B%20for%20professionals.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGigi%2C%20which%20recently%20rebranded%20from%20an%20AI-powered%20dating%20app%20to%20an%20%26quot%3BAI%20social%20connector%26quot%3B%20for%20everything%20from%20friendship%20to%20partnership%20to%20projects%2C%20per%20its%20Apple%20App%20Store%20listing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E(Patron%20is%20not%20an%20investor%20in%20either%20of%20these.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we're%20going%20to%20see%20more%20of%20those%20emerge%2C%26quot%3B%20Atherton%20said.%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20the%20wedge%20they%20start%20with%20is%20professional%2C%20but%20then%20they%20build%20your%20trust%2C%20and%20they%20start%20branching%20out%20more%20into%20friendship%2C%20hobbies%2C%20dating.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAtherton%20said%20the%20space%20is%20%26quot%3Bnascent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Patron%20is%20actively%20investing%20in%20its%20relationship%20tech%20thesis%2C%20Atherton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20alone%20in%20watching%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsumer-startups-watch-social-dating-ai-according-to-vc-investors-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estartups%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20this%20space.%20Other%20consumer-focused%20VCs%20have%20also%20expressed%20interest%20in%20backing%20startups%20that%20address%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnext-social-consumer-app-startups-vc-investors-ai-gen-z-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eloneliness%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20those%20that%20use%20AI%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226b7649b6-3ee8-46b9-ae82-d067f79e824f%5C%22%3ELooking%20for%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20consumer%20tech%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20VC%20firms%20have%20soured%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-consumer-tech-hub-startups-founders-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econsumer%20investments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Patron%20is%20hyper-focused%20on%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20Patron%20closed%20a%20%24100%20million%20fund%20and%20is%20investing%20in%20seed-stage%20consumer%20startups%20with%20%242%20million%20to%20%245%20million%20checks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20kind%20of%20look%20at%20this%20landscape%20of%20new%20consumer%20startups%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20gaming%2C%26quot%3B%20Atherton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20cofounders%2C%20Brian%20Cho%20and%20Jason%20Yeh%2C%20were%20former%20executives%20at%20Riot%20Games%2C%20and%20Atherton%20worked%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-discord%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDiscord%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20company%20acquired%20her%20community%20software%20startup%20Zyper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20build%20a%20consumer%20product%20that%20people%20want%20to%20spend%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20hours%20in%3F%26quot%3B%20Atherton%20said.%20%26quot%3BYour%20identity%20is%20tied%20to%20it%2C%20you%20have%20fun%20there%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20place%20to%20hang%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20Atherton%20published%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpatron.fund%2Fblog%2Ffuture-relationship-tech%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E%20post%20that%20detailed%20four%20categories%20(including%20her%20%26quot%3Brelationship%20OS%26quot%3B%20thesis)%20where%20she%20sees%20%26quot%3Bbreakout%20consumer%20businesses%20being%20b