ys-shopping-event-expands-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPrime%20Day%20lasts%20four%20days%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20July%208%20and%2011.%20That's%20longer%20than%20the%20event%20has%20run%20before%2C%20so%20the%20final%20results%20could%20differ%20depending%20on%20what%20shoppers%20buy%20in%20the%20final%20days%20of%20the%20sale.%20(Business%20Insider's%20Reviews%20team%20is%20also%20covering%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fprime-day-deals-2025-7-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20Prime%20Day%20deals%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20products%20and%20brands%20it%20has%20tested%20and%20reviewed.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Liquid%20IV%2C%20Dawn%20dish%20detergent%20and%20protein%20shakes%20were%20the%20next%20most-purchased%20Prime%20Day%20items%20by%20volume%2C%20according%20to%20Numerator.%20Amazon's%20Fire%20TV%20Stick%20%E2%80%94%20the%20fourth%20most-purchased%20item%20%E2%80%94%20was%20the%20most%20popular%20consumer%20electronic.%20Other%20frequently%20bought%20product%20categories%20so%20far%20include%20apparel%2C%20shoes%2C%20and%20home%20decor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShoppers%20are%20also%20buying%20lots%20of%20cheaper%20items.%20The%20average%20price%20per%20item%20so%20far%20this%20Prime%20Day%20is%20just%20over%20%2425%2C%20Numerator%20found.%20Two-thirds%20of%20everything%20sold%20so%20far%20on%20Prime%20Day%20cost%20shoppers%20less%20than%20%2420.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20clear%20difference%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.numerator.com%2Fpress%2Famazon-prime-day-early-results-are-numerator-reports%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efour%20years%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20when%20Amazon-branded%20electronics%2C%20such%20as%20the%20latest%20Echo%20Dot%20speaker%20and%20the%20Fire%20Tablet%2C%20dominated%20similar%20early%20results%20from%20Numerator.%20No%20household%20goods%20were%20in%20the%20top%20five%20most-purchased%20products%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrime%20Day%20shoppers%20may%20be%20spending%20cautiously%20given%20worries%20about%20tariff-induced%20price%20increases%20later%20this%20year%2C%20said%20Sky%20Canaves%2C%20principal%20analyst%20at%20EMARKETER%2C%20which%20shares%20an%20owner%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBusiness%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20stocking%20up%20on%20essentials%2C%20getting%20a%20head%20start%20on%20back-to-school%20and%20holiday%20shopping%2C%20and%20pulling%20up%20purchases%20of%20bigger-ticket%20items%20that%20may%20cost%20more%20later%20in%20the%20year%2C%20such%20as%20appliances%2C%26quot%3B%20Canaves%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220112be7c-a732-4e4c-b373-d0b92151dc96%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Fewer%20deals%2C%20but%20deeper%20discounts%5C%22%3EFewer%20deals%2C%20but%20deeper%20discounts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20report%20from%20Impact%20Analytics%20released%20Wednesday%20found%20that%20Amazon%20appears%20to%20be%20offering%20discounts%20on%20a%20narrower%20range%20of%20items%20than%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImpact%20found%20that%20last%20year%2C%20about%2040%25%20of%20Amazon%20products%20were%20discounted%20for%20Prime%20Day.%20Early%20results%20from%20this%20year%20show%20that%20the%20number%20has%20dropped%20by%20about%2024%20percentage%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20Amazon's%20discounts%20on%20many%20products%2C%20such%20as%20tools%2C%20lawn%20and%20garden%20supplies%2C%20and%20clothing%2C%20are%20deeper%20than%20in%202024.%20The%20analysis%20looked%20at%20discounts%20on%201%2C000%20top-selling%20products%20in%20the%20two%20days%20leading%20up%20to%20Prime%20Day%20as%20well%20as%20during%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20the%20sale%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmazon%20shifted%20to%20a%20more%20selective%2C%20margin-conscious%20strategy%2C%20likely%20shaped%20by%20tariff%20exposure%20and%20input%20cost%20pressures%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEMARKETER%20estimates%20that%20the%20four-day%20event%20will%20generate%20%2412.93%20billion%20in%20sales%20for%20Amazon.%20If%20Amazon%20had%20limited%20Prime%20Day%20to%2048%20hours%2C%20as%20it%20has%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20EMARKETER%20estimates%20sales%20would%20have%20been%20%248.95%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20shoppers'%20focus%20on%20cheaper%20essential%20items%2C%20they're%20already%20spending%20more%20overall%20than%20in%20previous%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENumerator%20found%20that%20roughly%20halfway%20into%20this%20year's%20event%20on%20Wednesday%20afternoon%2C%20average%20household%20spending%20on%20Amazon%20during%20Prime%20Day%20was%20%24126.26.%20That's%20up%20from%20about%20%2492%20at%20a%20similar%20point%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-amazon-prime-day-customers-buying-most-better-cheaper-discounts-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752167832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61faa12c4e4b5500188b9421%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-amazon-prime-day-customers-buying-most-better-cheaper-discounts-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Early%20results%20from%20Amazon's%20four-day%20Prime%20Day%20sale%20show%20shoppers%20are%20gravitating%20toward%20dish%20detergent%20and%20other%20essentials.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abitter%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Bitter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-amazon-prime-day-customers-buying-most-better-cheaper-discounts-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zomato%20founder%20buys%20apartment%20for%20%E2%82%B952.3%20cr%20in%20DLF%20Camellias%20in%20Gurugram%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752167630000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fzomato-founder-buys-a