en-garden-guide-grow-your-vegetables-and-herbs-monsoon-season-temperature-soil%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekitchen%20staple%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20many%20Indian%20households%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20during%20the%20rains.%20You%20may%20remember%20it%20from%20your%20mum%E2%80%99s%20curry%20pot%2C%20but%20this%20thorny%20green%20is%20gaining%20new%20life%20in%20home%20gardens%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKantola%20is%20well-suited%20for%20warm%2C%20humid%20weather%20and%20requires%20very%20little%20intervention%20once%20established.%20With%20the%20onset%20of%20monsoon%20providing%20ideal%20conditions%20for%20germination%20and%20growth%2C%20now%20is%20an%20excellent%20time%20to%20plant%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20step-by-step%20guide%20outlines%20everything%20beginners%20need%20to%20know%20%E2%80%94%20from%20sourcing%20seeds%20and%20preparing%20soil%20to%20supporting%20the%20vine%20and%20harvesting%20the%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20grow%20kantola%20in%2010%20easy%20steps%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Source%20the%20right%20seeds%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStart%20by%20getting%20quality%20%3Cem%3Ekantola%3C%2Fem%3E%20seeds%20or%20tuber%20roots%20from%20a%20local%20nursery%2C%20agro%20shop%2C%20or%20reliable%20online%20vendor.%20Look%20for%20heirloom%20or%20indigenous%20varieties.%20Kantola%20can%20be%20grown%20from%20seeds%20or%20from%20tuberous%20roots%3B%20tubers%20sprout%20quicker%2C%20but%20seeds%20are%20more%20readily%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__media%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F612Z27UTnOL._SL1382_-1752155964-500x910.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%