standard%20operating%20procedures%20during%20emergencies%20for%20pilots%20is%20to%20%3Cem%3Eaviate%2C%20navigate%2C%20and%20communicate%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Poonam%20says.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98Aviate%E2%80%99%20means%20that%20we%20need%20to%20fly%20the%20aircraft%2C%20%E2%80%98navigate%E2%80%99%20is%20about%20knowing%20where%20you%20are%20going%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98communicate%E2%80%99%20means%20staying%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20Air%20Traffic%20Controller%20(ATC).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoonam%20explains%20that%20pilots%20are%20trained%20to%20handle%20all%20kinds%20of%20emergencies%20%E2%80%94%20from%20engine%20failures%20and%20fires%20to%20rapid%20decompression%2C%20which%20happens%20when%20the%20cabin%20suddenly%20loses%20pressure.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20train%20for%20these%20situations%20regularly%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20the%20cabin%20crew%20is%20prepared%20to%20deal%20with%20medical%20emergencies%2C%20like%20if%20a%20passenger%20has%20a%20heart%20attack%20mid-flight.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-72-1752143069.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-72-1752143069.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-72-1752143069-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-72-1752143069-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-72-1752143069-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-72-1752143069-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-467132%5C%22%20h