ertainment%20or%20sustenance.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20an%20identity.%E2%80%9D%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-64-1752055684.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-64-1752055684-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-64-1752055684-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-64-1752055684-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-64-1752055684-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-466536%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDipali%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFood%20is%20not%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20entertainment%20or%20sustenance.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20an%20identity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20research%20and%20documentation%2C%20and%20bringing%20eyes%20to%20Rajasthani%20food%20via%20her%20informative%20Instagram%20videos%2C%20Dipali%20also%20curates%20pop-up%20travelling%20museums%2C%20which%20are%20filled%20with%20tangible%20things%20from%20across%20Rajasthan.%20There%20are%20ingredients%20and%20foods%20that%20people%20are%20free%20to%20taste%2C%20along%20with%20other%20components%20such%20as%20photo%20essays%2C%20audio%20stories%2C%20and%20artworks.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20Rajasthani%20people%20come%20and%20tell%20us%20that%20they%20have%20heard%20about%20these%20ingredients%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20first%20time%20seeing%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20creation%20is%20made%20of%20multiple%20components%2C%20keeping%20in%20mind%20that%20if%20I%E2%80%99m%20taking%20it%20to%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20say%2C%20Meghalaya%2C%20it%20should%20make%20the%20viewer