-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cem%3EIF.BE%20is%20a%20space%20where%20artists%20can%20converge%20and%20discuss%20ideas%20as%20well%20as%20come%20together%20to%20share%20their%20expertise%20on%20a%20range%20of%20different%20topics%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbico%20Ice%20Factory%20(as%20it%20was%20known%20then)%20enjoyed%20its%20popularity%20for%20decades%20before%20a%20factory%20in%20New%20Bombay%20took%20over%20operations.%20%E2%80%9CIce%20first%20came%20to%20India%20on%20a%20ship%20from%20Boston%20in%20the%201800s%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20ice%2C%20history%20tells%20us%2C%20was%20stored%20in%20ice%20houses%20in%20Mumbai%20but%20India%E2%80%99s%20heat%20posed%20a%20challenge.%20So%2C%20businessmen%20Nanabhoy%20Byramjee%20Jeejeebhoy%20and%20JA%20Forbes%20launched%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20first%20ice%20factory%20in%20Ballard%20Estate%20in%201878.%20It%20was%20christened%20%E2%80%98Bombay%20Ice%20Manufacturing%20Co%E2%80%99%20before%20being%20rebranded%20as%20%E2%80%98Ambico%20Ice%20Factory%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%202019%2C%20when%20Malik%20first%20set%20sight%20on%20the%20building%2C%20he%20acquired%20it%20but%20with%20no%20plans%20to%20renovate%20or%20repurpose%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366166%2Fcossimbazar-palace-of-roys-rajbari-murshidabad-west-bengal-ancestral-palaces-heritage-hotel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epiece%20of%20history%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20banyan%20tree%2C%20however%2C%20would%20etch%20an%20image%20in%20Malik%E2%80%99s%20mind%20that%20would%20eventually%20become%20the%20seed%20that%20would%20reinvigorate%20the%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20had%20no%20idea%2C%20whatsoever%2C%20of%20either%20acquiring%20such%20a%20space%20or%20wanting%20to%20do%20something%20with%20it.%20But%20the%20image%20of%20the%20banyan%20tree%20stayed%20with%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20A%20few%20months%20later%2C%20Malik%20found%20himself%20saying%20a%20%E2%80%98yes%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20project%2C%20joined%20by%20Abhijit%20Mehta%2C%20Arjun%20Malik%2C%20and%20Amrita%20Malik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20Malik%20Architecture%2C%20the%20team%20embarked%20on%20the%20quest%20to%20give%20the%20ice%20factory%20a%20second%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20IF.BE%20is%20a%2010%2C000-square-foot%20space%20that%20boasts%20five%20sections%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98The%20Banyan%20Tree%20Caf%C3%A9%E2%80%99%3B%20%E2%80%98The%20Substation%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F145074%2Flibrary-books-ruchi-dhona-children-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereading%20room%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20shop%20for%20architectural%20instruments%20and%20books%3B%20the%20%E2%80%98Ice%20Factory%E2%80%99%20designed%20for%20performances%3B%20%E2%80%98The%20Cathedral%E2%80%99%20where%20the%20bulk%20of%20exhibitions%20take%20place%3B%20and%20the%20fine%20dining%20Indian%20restaurant%2C%20Native%20Bombay%2C%20where%20guests%20fuel%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIF.BE%3A%20Stitching%20sustainability%20with%20history%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20of%20the%20project%20and%20the%20addition%20of%20the%20dot%20between%20the%20words%20do%20not%20skip%20my%20attention.%20Elaborating%20on%20it%2C%20Malik%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20dot%20%E2%80%94%20that%20gap%20between%20%E2%80%98if%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98be%E2%80%99%20symbolises%20time.%20If%20and%20be%20%E2%80%94%20the%20possibilities.%E2%80%9D%20And%20this%20is%20essentially%20the%20message%20that%20the%20architects%20have%20attempted%20to%20convey%2C%20the%20freedom%20that%20comes%20with%20the%20arts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Malik%20details%20the%20restoration%2C%20one%20thing%20is%20evident%3A%20the%20rendering%20was%20rooted%20in%20h