e%20stability%20to%20the%20walls.%20It%20also%20took%20care%20of%20the%20seismic%20aspects.%20We%20restored%20the%20wood%20and%20the%20brick.%20The%20only%20new%20material%20that%20we%20bought%20on%20site%20was%20a%20very%20small%20quantity%20of%20lightweight%20steel%2C%20which%20was%20used%20to%20cover%20the%20courtyard%20space%20and%20for%20the%20galvanised%20iron%20roofs.%E2%80%9D%20It%E2%80%99s%20almost%20as%20if%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20past%20gave%20way%20to%20its%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20IF.BE%20is%20an%20architecturally%20striking%20oasis%20of%20sustainability%20with%20detail%20in%20each%20corner.%20But%2C%20Malik%20says%20he%20is%20biased%20towards%20the%20banyan%20tree.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20symbolic%2C%20almost%20a%20metaphor%20for%20a%20seed%20of%20transformation%2C%20something%20that%20IF.BE%20has%20been%20through.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%3A%20Kamal%20Malik%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751981729000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-55-1751977795.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D465866%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kamal%20Malik%20transformed%20Mumbai's%20historic%20Ice%20Factory%2C%20once%20an%201878%20ice%20production%20site%2C%20into%20the%20vibrant%20IF.BE%20creative%20hub.%20The%2010%2C000-square-foot%20space%20now%20features%20art%20venues%2C%20workshops%2C%20and%20a%20caf%C3%A9.%20Malik%20preserved%20the%20building's%20history%20while%20integrating%20sustainability%2C%20making%20IF.BE%20a%20modern%20cultural%20landmark.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F465866%2Fasia-oldest-145-year-old-ice-factory-if-be-kamal-malik%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20a%20Flood-Hit%20Slum%20in%20Kol